<i>noun</i>: 패륜 [패ː륜], 불륜 [불륜] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>패륜 [패ː륜]</dt><br>
<dd>immorality; obliquity</dd><br>
<dd>인간으로서 마땅히 해야 할 도리에 어긋남. 또는 그런 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of doing something against the morality that a person should have, or such a behavior.</dd><br>
<dt>불륜 [불륜]</dt><br>
<dd>immorality; obliquity</dd><br>
<dd>사람으로서 마땅히 지켜야 할 바른 행동에서 벗어난 데가 있음.</dd><br>
<dd>Behavior which is against morality that a person should have.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>